channel.title: Webclient error
channel.description:
Hello everyone, so i have been working on my webclient for the past couple days and i have finally got part of it to work.. (before it would just white screen) But anyways... now i can't figure out what i am doing wrong. The cache has already downloaded, but then after it did that this happened...
[img]http://gyazo.com/0d115e6a9a123384246d58adeb6930e4.png?1326556859[/img] This is what comes up right before the picture that i am posting next: [img]http://gyazo.com/abdf1553280876a0c41c72c9cc55c810.png?1326556900[/img]
I have followed everything from someones tutorial on a different forum and it was a good tutorial too. (i don't know if i'm aloud to post the link to tutorial or not so i just wont)
But anyways... you guys got any ideas? Thank you :)
EDIT: and yes i have jarred client and uploaded files to dropbox.
no one seems to help in client section so thought i would post here...
